ActNational Aboriginal Economic Development Board Order
PrecisReapointment of CHARLES S. COFFEY of North York, Ontario, to be a member of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years; and designate CHARLES S. COFFEY as Vice-Chairperson of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board.
